martial_arts.title: Martial Arts
martial_arts.description: Immerse yourself in a disciplined artistry, be entertained by fantastic gravity-defying feats, and finally understand those Wu-Tang references.

257167.title: City Hunter
257167.description: P.I. Ryu Saeba’s first impulse is to turn down a job to find the beautiful runaway daughter of a publishing tycoon—until he sees a picture of her.

257298.title: The Protector
257298.description: A pair of New York City detectives are sent to Hong Kong to go on the hunt for a drug lord who has kidnapped the daughter of a former associate.

272763.title: Crime Story
272763.description: Inspector Eddie Chan fights mobsters, corruption, and his own personal demons as he searches for a kidnapped business man in Hong Kong and Taiwan.

279388.title: Bushido Man
279388.description: Toramaru, lord of integrated martial arts Mugen-ga-ryu, ends his training journey and visits his master, Gensai.

282408.title: Bruce Lee: The Man, The Myth
282408.description: A highly fictionalized biography of the famous Bruce Lee, this movie traces his college life, his marriage to Linda Lee, his relationship with his master, and his untimely death.

284003.title: Street Fighter Alpha
284003.description: Brought together by the mysterious death of their martial arts master, Ken and Ryu must overcome a momentous challenge unlike any other.

302433.title: Kickboxer 2
302433.description: Fighter Tong Po will stop at nothing to challenge one retired kickboxer, who must recover to face the man who injured him and killed his brothers.

302434.title: Kickboxer 4: The Aggressor
302434.description: A wrongfully-imprisoned martial arts fighter is released under the condition that he helps the police take down a vicious drug lord.

302507.title: TKO
302507.description: In a city where image is everything, the criminal underworld holds a fight tournament where legends are born and those who own them run the streets.

303002.title: American Ninja 4
303002.description: Two martial arts fighters are sent to stop a terrorist and a group of ninjas from blowing up New York City in this action thriller.

304780.title: Kickboxer 3
304780.description: David Sloan travels to Rio de Janeiro and puts his life on the line as he confronts a gang of terrorists in order to free a kidnapped girl.

307753.title: Kickboxer
307753.description: After a kickboxing champ is paralyzed fighting Thailand’s top fighter, his brother vows vengeance but must learn Muay Thai to fight back.

313912.title: The Sword Identity
313912.description: During the Ming Dynasty, one man is forced into a series of new-form kung fu fights to prove the invincibility of his authentic, Chinese-made sword.

313924.title: Wushu
313924.description: A decade after graduating, five students from an elite martial arts academy reunite to battle an evil master who runs a child-abduction ring.

313929.title: Four Dragons
313929.description: Four “brothers” come together in the Malaysian mining colony of Kinta for better lives, but are forced to unleash the art of Wushu against corruption.

314835.title: Kickboxer 5: Redemption
314835.description: A retired kickboxer goes on a mission to avenge the brutal death of his promising student, targeting the leader of an underworld kickboxing league.

326867.title: Bangkok Assassins
326867.description: Kidnapped as children and trained in martial arts, four teenagers unite to avenge the death of their beloved Shaolin Kung Fu master.

358884.title: Yasmine
358884.description: Tired of her school and fed up in an underdog Silat club, she decidesto take matters into her own hands and start leading the team.

376059.title: Covert Operation
376059.description: When a rescue mission for a British operative in North Korea goes wrong, Gabriel must take on an entire military installation to bring everyone home.

376068.title: Muay Thai Fighter
376068.description: When a childhood boxing club falls apart, three friends start down a dangerous path when they begin fighting underground for money.

376464.title: Lawless Kingdom
376464.description: Four detectives with superhuman abilities must solve a series of murders after discovering clues to an unsolved case. But can they survive?

417610.title: White Tiger
417610.description: After a Chinese drug lord murders his partner, a tough DEA agent teams up with a mysterious beauty and makes an uneasy alliance to exact revenge.

449365.title: Kung Fu Traveler
449365.description: A hostile alien race has overtaken Earth and humans are under attack with only one person who can fight the forces of the past to save the future.

456906.title: Ninja
456906.description: A ninja-in-training returns to New York to protect a legendary chest of weapons from high-flying assassins that test his skills at every turn.

461204.title: The Forbidden Kingdom
461204.description: A mystical staff transports an American teen to China, where he joins a band of martial-arts warriors to free the imprisoned Monkey King.

461512.title: Death Trance
461512.description: A fearsome samurai hungry for an ultimate challenge must do battle with a powerful temple monk intent on preventing ultimate worldly destruction.

463726.title: Blackbelt
463726.description: A powerful cast of martial-arts fighters star in this story of an ex-cop who must protect a singer from a psychotic serial killer.

465003.title: Bloodfist
465003.description: To find his brother's killer, a retired kickboxer enters an illegal tournament in Manila where the fight doesn't end until someone is dead.

469286.title: Firecracker
469286.description: A buxom martial-arts master dishes out justice to ferocious gangsters while investigating the mysterious disappearance of her sister.

490122.title: Sakura Killer
490122.description: After ninja thieves steal a secret gene-splicing formula, a U.S. colonel sends two of his men to Taiwan to keep the ninjas from selling it to Russia.

494963.title: Mantis Fists and Tiger Claws of Shaolin
494963.description: A stranger searching for his long-lost sister becomes both a hero and a murder suspect, when he defends a woman from thugs, who later wind up dead.

497116.title: Legend of the Red Dragon
497116.description: It takes a father and son team to battle the forces of evil throughout China, fighting with honor to defend the weak through fast-motion kung fu.

497642.title: Fist of Fury
497642.description: Bruce Lee stars in this iconic action film about a student who fights for the honor of the oppressed Chinese people and to avenge his master’s murder

499293.title: Ong Bak 3: The Final Battle
499293.description: Picking up where the saga left off, Tien, who was captured and beaten, returns to the Kana Khone village, to learn new skills and face a final duel.

500729.title: New Fist of Fury
500729.description: Action-packed martial arts drama about a young man out to prove his Kung-Fu expertise while seeking revenge after his grandfather is killed.

500953.title: Beyond Fear
500953.description: A martial arts expert working as a wilderness guide must defend her tour group against two killers out to retrieve an incriminating videotape.

501418.title: Ninja: Shadow of a Tear
501418.description: When the life of a martial arts master is shattered by his wife’s brutal murder, he enlists an old friend to sharpen his skills and seek revenge.

504091.description: A gentle giant joins two sisters after being attacked on vacation in Thailand, becoming a raging martial artist anytime he eats a spicy delicacy.

505025.title: Kung Fu Killer
505025.description: After a martial arts instructor kills a man by mistake, he is imprisoned, until the police need his help taking down a vengeful killer.

506494.title: Kung Fu Yoga
506494.description: Two professors team up to locate a lost treasure and embark on an adventure that takes them from a Tibetan ice cave to a mountain temple in India.

507966.title: Shaolin
507966.description: A general, still recovering from a devastating betrayal, meets an eccentric cook who teaches him the secret to perfecting his martial arts skills.

516856.title: Shaolin Drunk Fighter
516856.description: The murder of a young man’s family by a group of ruthless martial art masters becomes his obsession in seeking ultimate revenge on them all.

518146.title: The Shaolin Drunk Monkey
518146.description: A conceited martial arts master is challenged to a deadly duel by an opponent he assumes is less than worthy.

519047.title: Sun Dragon
519047.description: When a Black Panther's family is wiped out by a ruthless band of assassins, he sets out to avenge their murder with the help of a martial arts master.

520095.title: Cantonen Iron Kung Fu

520214.title: Kung Fu Killer (English Dubbed)
520214.description: A wrongly imprisoned kung fu master is offered his freedom in exchange for helping the police catch a serial killer targeting martial arts experts.

521033.title: Dragon
521033.description: The quiet life of a village craftsman, who makes paper, is irrevocably shattered by the arrival of two notorious gangsters in the local general store.

526566.title: Vengeance of an Assassin

536464.description: A compilation of movie trailers, behind-the-scenes footage and action-packed film clips from the greatest martial arts flicks of the 1970s.

539724.description: In a lawless city where gangs rule the streets, a fighter seeks revenge against a gang for murdering his brother.

541309.title: 2099: The Soldier Protocol
541309.description: A biotech experiment conducted by the military inside a prison gives an inmate with paralysis the ability to walk again, but at a torturous price.

543991.title: Circle of Iron

551209.title: He Has Nothing but Kung Fu

551211.description: A common disciple at the Shaolin Temple must battle against a brutal tyrant and his army of martial artists.

551219.title: Iron Monkey Strikes Back (Duel at the Tiger Village)

551250.title: Born Invincible

551254.title: Seven Commandments of Kung Fu

551258.title: 36 Deadly Styles

552694.title: The Dragon Unleashed

557486.title: Return of the Sister Street Fighter

560515.title: Ninja Warriors From Beyond (Ninja Death Squad)

560676.description: While visiting his estranged daughter at a nightclub, a cop must spring into action, as an elaborate kidnapping plot unfolds right before his eyes.

560841.title: Tai Chi Hero (Dubbed)
560841.description: The Tai Chi master who saved his village in the past plans to marry his beautiful teacher, who has her own plan to weaken his power with each lesson.

560873.title: Ip Man: The Final Fight (Dubbed)
560873.description: In postwar Hong Kong, a real-life Wing Chun grandmaster rises to action once more, as kung fu rivals draw him into a dark, dangerous underworld.

560875.description: An undercover cop infiltrates a ruthless crime syndicate and risks everything to shield his life and family, after the boss vows to kill all traitors.

561518.title: Adventure at Shaolin
561518.description: Martial arts dazzler about the founder of Tai Chi and his quest to become an expert fighter as he learns two timeless techniques of self-defense.

562120.title: Once Upon a Time in Shanghai
562120.description: A peaceful peasant tries to strike it rich in Shanghai, but when he befriends the boss of a menacing gang, he must use his kung fu skills and fight

568084.description: The only survivor of a massacre in a Manchurian province trains at a Shaolin Temple where the Monkey Fist methods he learns will demolish the killers.

574796.description: When a sleepy Chinese village is threatened by a dangerous gang, a kung fu master trains his young pupil to start picking off its members, one-by-one.

576587.title: The Man From Kathmandu

585806.title: Memories of the Sword
585806.description: To avenge the death of her mother, a young woman in medieval Korea will have to face off against one of the most brutal tyrants of the Goryo Dynasty.

588486.title: Merantau Dubbed

588490.title: Chocolate (Dubbed)

589817.title: Saving General Yang (English Dub)
589817.description: A battle of intense loyalty forged by family love is set when seven sons fight a massive army in a cross-country rescue mission to save their father.

590211.title: The Knight of Shadows (English Dub)
590211.description: A demon hunter is enlisted by a village to save the lives of young girls who have been kidnapped by dark forces that feed on their souls.

590263.title: The Guillotines (English Dub)
590263.description: A group of secret assassins, The Guillotines, are betrayed by their new rulers and exiled to an island where a squad of gun shooters comes for them.

591171.title: Kung Fu Yoga (Spanish Dub)
591171.description: La búsqueda del tesoro de Magadha lleva a un profesor de China y a una de la India a una cueva de hielo tibetana, a Dubai y a un templo de la India.

591361.title: Legend of the Tsunami Warrior (Dubbed)

591376.title: Rise of the Legend (Dubbed)
591376.description: An extraordinarily powerful martial artist returns to where his father was assassinated to free the people from his nemesis, a ruthless crime lord.

592891.title: Sworn to Justice
592891.description: After attackers kill her sister and nephew, a psychologist, who possesses the gift of ESP, becomes a defense witness by day and an avenger by night.

592893.title: Red Sun Rising

602160.description: After growing up in the Shaolin Temple, a budding martial artist studies the importance of patience and mercy and takes on the Eight Masters.

602180.title: Monkey Fist, Floating Snake
602180.description: After a martial arts expert accepts a disciple, the student works hard to train and become a master of a specialized form of kung fu.

602187.title: Six Directions Boxing

604310.title: Robin-B-Hood
604310.description: Thongs and Octopus grow attached to the baby they kidnapped for their landlord, which leads to complications in handing the him over.

604316.title: Seven Swords
604316.description: Seven exceptional warriors band together to protect a village from bounty hunters.

610633.title: The 47 Ronin (Pt. 1)

611090.description: La envidia le corroe al despiadado Chu y quiere apoderarse del exitoso negocio de la familia Leung valiéndose de sus dotes marciales.

611117.title: 18 Fatal Strikes
611117.description: When an abbot monk is injured and ends up in the home of two young men, the three become targets of the Ching Army and its evil leader, Wong Wu Ti.

614736.title: Iron Monkey 2
614736.description: Action star Donnie Yen stars in this sequel where he fights a lethal assassin in China who has assembled a gang of vicious weapons smugglers.

619654.title: Ip Man (English Dub)
619654.description: Tells the story of the brutality of the 1939 Japanese occupation of China through the eyes of the Wing Chun grandmaster who rose to fight against it.

619656.title: Ip Man 2 (English Dub)
619656.description: When the Wing Chun grandmaster moves to Hong Kong to open a school for the next generation of fighters, he’s forced to take on a corrupt cabal.

619660.title: Ip Man 3 (English Dub)
619660.description: Hong Kong, 1959. A crooked real estate developer leads a band of gangsters in a property coup that can only be stopped by the Wing Chun grandmaster.

619662.title: Kickboxer: Retaliation
619662.description: Following a Las Vegas match, an MMA champ is abducted and sent to a Bangkok prison where he must fight for his freedom against a 400-pound killer.

620085.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
620085.description: Action icon Donnie Yen stars as a super cop who becomes depressed and obese after a break-up and just before he gets a murder case to save his job.

622697.title: Crippled Kung Fu Boxer
622697.description: When his kung fu gym is hijacked by the Hunchback and his gang, a student trains in the art of the Crippled Fist in an attempt to avenge his master.

623238.title: The Protector
623238.description: When his family’s elephants are stolen from the Bangkok jungle, a young fighter travels to Australia to retrieve them from the dangerous Thai mafia.

626674.title: Chinese Hercules
626674.description: A muscular martial arts warrior tries to leave his past behind and becomes a dock worker, but the cruel owner’s iron fist leads him to fight again.

626712.title: Shaolin Temple
626712.description: Two brothers train at the revered and superior Shaolin Temple during the Manchu Dynasty to take revenge on their father’s killer.

626742.title: Master of the Flying Guillotine
626742.description: An evil and bling Kung Fu master travels to a martial arts competition with his secret weapon that can decapitate any one-armed foe he sees.

626765.title: American Fighter
626765.description: A young wrestler is forced to get gritty and stay strong when he enters an underground fighting ring to pay for his mother’s medical treatments.

626783.title: Young Hero of Shaolin
626783.description: The 1979 martial arts classic about a legendary fighter who was trained by his mother before he went into the Shaolin Temple as an undefeated master.

626822.title: Method Man (Fearless Young Boxer)
626822.description: A young man poses as a touring acrobat with a performing company so that he can learn greater martial arts skills to vanquish his father’s killer.

626871.title: Kung Fu From Beyond the Grave

626972.title: Death Duel of Kung Fu
626972.description: Two great fighters clash in an epic battle of supremacy as Ching Ming prepares for all-out war between his fighters and Taiwan’s kung fu artists.

626979.title: Dance of the Drunken Mantis
626979.description: A young martial arts master must face off against a fierce rival named Rubber Legs who has blended two deadly fighting styles for ultimate domination.

627610.title: Fearless Hyena

627687.title: Return of the Kung Fu Dragon

627690.title: Ninja Death 3
627690.description: A blind fortune teller and his trio of fighters go against a seemingly indestructible crew including a Grandmaster, Devil Mask, and Infinite Ninjas.

627736.title: Snake the Tiger the Crane
627736.description: An Emperor’s daughter and a fierce warrior with one arm team together to defeat the latest invaders coming to destroy their kingdom.

629852.title: Iron Swallow
629852.description: A fierce female vigilante, Iron Swallow, wields her own lethal fighting style and goes even harder as a mystery killer tries to set her up for a fall.

629853.title: Lady Iron Monkey
629853.description: A young woman raised by apes, who is an expert kung fu fighter, is deceived by the false romantic attraction of a prince who uses her for her powers.

629854.title: Shaolin Master and the Kid
629854.description: The work of a federal officer in Hong Kong becomes personal when he’s assigned to take down every one of his late brother’s evil assassins.

629859.title: The Fierce Boxer
629859.description: Epic revenge fable of classic kung fu fighting involving an orphaned boy who grows up to master White Crane boxing to vanquish his father’s murderer

639597.title: Shogun's Ninja

639644.title: Twin Dragons
639644.description: The lives of identical twin brothers separated at birth comically converge when the symphony conductor and cunning mechanic cross paths as adults.

646730.title: Fists of Fury
646730.description: A kung-fu fighter discovers the ice factory where he works is a front for the same drug trafficking ring responsible for the deaths of his relatives.

649977.title: Master Z: Ip Man Legacy (English Dub)

649979.title: Shadow (English Dub)
649979.description: The multiple-award-winning action film about a kingdom commander facing betrayal at all angles who has a lookalike shadow who can slay his foes.

654072.title: The Warrior's Way
654072.description: The world's finest warrior-assassin leaves Japan to find an old friend in the American Badlands rather than kill the infant queen of a rival clan.

659212.title: Rumble
659212.description: A former MMA star is forced to take on the deadliest of underground fights, in order to save the love of his life from a cartel’s criminal mastermind.

659271.title: Gambling for Head

659522.title: Martial Arts History Museum Biography: Michelle Manu
659522.description: The museum honors senior black belt Michelle Manu, considered the leading advocate for promoting the Hawaiian art of Kaihewalu Lua across the globe.

659528.title: Martial Arts History Museum Biography: Ernie Reyes
659528.description: The museum honors the Great Grandmaster, founder of the West Coast World Martial Arts Association and inductee into the Black Belt Hall of Fame.

664251.title: Lord of the Streets

665431.title: Black and White Swordsmen

667081.title: Real Kung Fu of Shaolin

671826.title: Lady Bloodfight

673405.title: Exit the Tiger, Enter the Dragon

673874.description: Kung fu expert Ma Ta must come to the rescue of his friend Hou Hsian-Shan who is being tortured by casino guards after he was caught cheating.

673876.title: The Deadly Duo

673877.title: Dragon Lee vs. the Five Brothers
673877.description: On route to deliver the names of anti-Ching revolutionaries to his Ming leaders, Dragon Lee encounters resistance from a group of Ching loyalists.

673880.title: Fighting Ace

673890.title: Mantis Under Falcon's Claws
